README.md
     1вҶ’# dotenv
     5вҶ’Dotenv is a zero-dependency module that loads environment variables from a `.env` file into [`process.env`](https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/process.html#process_process_env). Storing configuration in the environment separate from code is based on [The Twelve-Factor App](https://12factor.net/config) methodology.
     6вҶ’
     7вҶ’[Watch the tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YtkZR0NFd1g)
     8вҶ’
     9вҶ’&nbsp;
    10вҶ’
    11вҶ’## Usage
    13вҶ’Install it.
    14вҶ’
    15вҶ’```sh
    16вҶ’npm install dotenv --save
    17вҶ’```
    18вҶ’
    19вҶ’Create a `.env` file in the root of your project:
    20вҶ’
    21вҶ’```ini
    22вҶ’# .env
    23вҶ’S3_BUCKET="YOURS3BUCKET"
    24вҶ’SECRET_KEY="YOURSECRETKEYGOESHERE"
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    39вҶ’## Advanced
    43вҶ’Import with [ES6](#how-do-i-use-dotenv-with-import):
    44вҶ’
    45вҶ’```javascript
    46вҶ’import 'dotenv/config'
    47вҶ’```
    48вҶ’
    49вҶ’ES6 import if you need to set config options:
    50вҶ’
    51вҶ’```javascript
    52вҶ’import dotenv from 'dotenv'
    53вҶ’dotenv.config({ path: '/custom/path/to/.env' })
    54вҶ’```
      вҶ’вҖҰ
   319вҶ’## Agents
   323вҶ’> Software is changing, and dotenv must change with itвҖ”that is why I built [agentic secret storage (AS2)](https://dotenvx.com/as2). Agents run code without humans at terminals, so plaintext `.env` files are the wrong primitive.
   324вҶ’>
   325вҶ’> AS2 is built for autonomous software: encrypted by default, zero console access, and cryptographyвҖ‘first delivery that keeps operators out of the loop.
   326вҶ’>
   327вҶ’> It is backed by [Vestauth](https://github.com/vestauth/vestauth), the trusted, pioneering auth layer for agentsвҖ”giving each agent a cryptographic identity so requests are signed with private keys and verified with public keys. No shared secrets to leak.
   328вҶ’>
   329вҶ’> It's what I'm using now. - [motdotla](https://mot.la)
   330вҶ’
   331вҶ’### Quickstart
   333вҶ’Install vestauth and initialize your agent.
   334вҶ’
   335вҶ’```bash
   336вҶ’npm i -g vestauth
   337вҶ’
   338вҶ’vestauth agent init
   339вҶ’```
      вҶ’вҖҰ
